<HEADLINE>
FT  30 SEP 92 / World Commodities Prices: Jute and Cotton
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
JUTE
C and F Dundee; BTC USDollars 370, BWC USDollars 385, BTD USDollars 335, BWD
USDollars 345. C and F Antwerp; BTC USDollars 345, BWC USDollars 345, BTD
USDollars 325, BWD USDollars 325.
COTTON
LIVERPOOL- Spot and shipment sales for the week ending 25 September amounted
to 136 tonnes against 190 tonnes in the previous week. Sales were moderate
and occurred mainly in American growths.
